    <h2>Garden Veggie Pizza</h2>
<img src="images/pizza.jpg" alt="Pizza">
<p><strong>Prep Time:</strong> 45 mins | <strong>Difficulty:</strong> Easy</p>
<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<ul><li>Dough, Tomato sauce, Mozzarella, Olives, Corn</li></ul>
<h3>Steps</h3>
<ol><li>Roll dough. <li>Apply sauce/toppings. <li>Bake at 220°C for 15 mins.</ol>